freelance thinker and consultant

00:21:22.350 --> 00:21:23.820 align:middle line:90%
and writer.

00:21:23.820 --> 00:21:27.230 align:middle line:84%
So I had many second
chances in a way.

00:21:27.230 --> 00:21:29.960 align:middle line:84%
I have been always
impatient in the sense

00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:33.290 align:middle line:84%
