the same thing year after year.

00:21:33.290 --> 00:21:35.390 align:middle line:84%
I was inquiring,
looking forward,

00:21:35.390 --> 00:21:39.230 align:middle line:84%
trying to find out who I am,
what the world is around me.

00:21:39.230 --> 00:21:45.530 align:middle line:84%
And I managed to get it as
a basis actually for living.

00:21:45.530 --> 00:21:50.570 align:middle line:84%
I never lived, I never worked
simply just to get a paycheck.

00:21:50.570 --> 00:21:52.610 align:middle line:90%
Maybe this sounds selfish.

