Institute of New
Paradigm Research

00:22:17.220 --> 00:22:20.060 align:middle line:84%
and carry forward this
work in such a way

00:22:20.060 --> 00:22:23.570 align:middle line:84%
that it would benefit not
only us to live from one day

00:22:23.570 --> 00:22:25.730 align:middle line:84%
