as it were because I
had my piano practice

00:23:23.110 --> 00:23:25.090 align:middle line:84%
sessions in the
morning with my mother,

00:23:25.090 --> 00:23:28.690 align:middle line:84%
walks with my uncle in
the park in the afternoon,

00:23:28.690 --> 00:23:32.210 align:middle line:84%
talking about things
like understanding

00:23:32.210 --> 00:23:35.100 align:middle line:84%
in the world, things
like living with nature

00:23:35.100 --> 00:23:38.570 align:middle line:84%
and this kind of thing, which is
very unusual for a small child.

00:23:38.570 --> 00:23:41.210 align:middle line:84%
I thought I forgot
all these things

00:23:41.210 --> 00:23:44.060 align:middle line:84%
until I was in my
late teens when

00:23:44.060 --> 00:23:48.740 align:middle line:84%
I was having quite a successful
concert career in New York

00:23:48.740 --> 00:23:51.140 align:middle line:84%
City with Life
articles appearing

00:23:51.140 --> 00:23:53.990 align:middle line:84%
on me in "Life Magazine,"
in "Time," and in "Newsweek"

00:23:53.990 --> 00:23:55.140 align:middle line:90%
and so on.

00:23:55.140 --> 00:23:58.220 align:middle line:84%
And then all of a sudden,
this idea cropped up,

00:23:58.220 --> 00:24:00.330 align:middle line:90%
but why am I doing this?

00:24:00.330 --> 00:24:02.250 align:middle line:90%
What am I doing?

00:24:02.250 --> 00:24:05.780 align:middle line:84%
And then these are
the questions that you

00:24:05.780 --> 00:24:09.780 align:middle line:84%
ask when you turn to
science and to philosophy.

00:24:09.780 --> 00:24:11.640 align:middle line:90%
So I turned that way.

00:24:11.640 --> 00:24:13.880 align:middle line:90%
I started attending courses.

00:24:13.880 --> 00:24:17.600 align:middle line:84%
I started cultivating friends
who had similar questions,

00:24:17.600 --> 00:24:21.930 align:middle line:84%
asking these questions, trying
to set out answers of my own.

00:24:21.930 --> 00:24:24.800 align:middle line:84%
And then by a fortunate
coincidence or perhaps not

00:24:24.800 --> 00:24:27.770 align:middle line:84%
a coincidence, but
it seems like that,

00:24:27.770 --> 00:24:30.680 align:middle line:84%
these notes got
published as a book,

00:24:30.680 --> 00:24:33.660 align:middle line:84%
even though I didn't have
any background in philosophy

00:24:33.660 --> 00:24:34.460 align:middle line:90%
and science.

00:24:34.460 --> 00:24:38.030 align:middle line:84%
My degree came as a child
prodigy when I was 15 years old.

00:24:38.030 --> 00:24:41.420 align:middle line:84%
I got an artist degree in
music at the Franz Liszt

00:24:41.420 --> 00:24:43.730 align:middle line:90%
Academy in Budapest.

00:24:43.730 --> 00:24:46.100 align:middle line:84%
But I had no academic
qualifications.

00:24:46.100 --> 00:24:48.770 align:middle line:84%
And yet when I wrote this
book and was published,

00:24:48.770 --> 00:24:51.440 align:middle line:84%
I got an invitation from
the Philosophy Department

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:56.950 align:middle line:84%
in Yale University to come and
give seminars on this thinking

00:24:56.950 --> 00:24:58.095 align:middle line:90%
on my ideas.

00:24:58.095 --> 00:24:58.970 align:middle line:90%
So I went over there.

00:24:58.970 --> 00:25:03.060 align:middle line:84%
And I was launched then on a
career in the academic world,

00:25:03.060 --> 00:25:06.430 align:middle line:84%
going from there to
various other universities.

00:25:06.430 --> 00:25:10.020 align:middle line:84%
And so it's something
that I just followed.

00:25:10.020 --> 00:25:12.180 align:middle line:84%
And it's not because
it was prescribed.

00:25:12.180 --> 00:25:14.100 align:middle line:84%
It was something
that is happening

00:25:14.100 --> 00:25:20.730 align:middle line:84%
to me, coming to me from the
experience of music as a child.

00:25:20.730 --> 00:25:24.900 align:middle line:84%
From the age of nine, I was
playing concerts solo and also

00:25:24.900 --> 00:25:26.220 align:middle line:90%
with orchestra.

00:25:26.220 --> 00:25:32.290 align:middle line:84%
And performing to a public
with a group of musicians

00:25:32.290 --> 00:25:35.230 align:middle line:84%
who follow you, who
become one with you

00:25:35.230 --> 00:25:38.630 align:middle line:84%
is such an incredible
experience.

00:25:38.630 --> 00:25:43.390 align:middle line:84%
It's a feeling sense of being
fulfilled or being one or being

00:25:43.390 --> 00:25:45.100 align:middle line:90%
carried forward.

00:25:45.100 --> 00:25:46.990 align:middle line:90%
It's difficult to describe.

00:25:46.990 --> 00:25:49.390 align:middle line:90%
But that's what motivated me.

00:25:49.390 --> 00:25:52.990 align:middle line:84%
That's what I've been
searching for in science also.

00:25:52.990 --> 00:25:56.290 align:middle line:84%
Wherever I see, I
search for that oneness,

00:25:56.290 --> 00:26:01.900 align:middle line:84%
for that interaction for
this collaboration, which

00:26:01.900 --> 00:26:06.190 align:middle line:84%
makes the body, a living
body, makes it whole.

00:26:06.190 --> 00:26:10.940 align:middle line:84%
A society becomes healthy if
it has this collaboration.

00:26:10.940 --> 00:26:12.640 align:middle line:90%
I'm searching for that.

00:26:12.640 --> 00:26:15.100 align:middle line:84%
And I try to
contribute by showing

00:26:15.100 --> 00:26:17.170 align:middle line:90%
that nature operates like that.

00:26:17.170 --> 00:26:19.240 align:middle line:90%
The universe is like that.

00:26:19.240 --> 00:26:21.410 align:middle line:84%
Even the universe,
as we saw before,

00:26:21.410 --> 00:26:23.800 align:middle line:84%
is an Akashic field where
all things are connected,

00:26:23.800 --> 00:26:25.510 align:middle line:90%
all things are conserved.

00:26:25.510 --> 00:26:30.490 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, I feel that this
is based on what I experience,

00:26:30.490 --> 00:26:32.440 align:middle line:90%
what I've always experienced.

00:26:32.440 --> 00:26:35.120 align:middle line:84%
And I want to cultivate
this experience.

00:26:35.120 --> 00:26:39.160 align:middle line:84%
It is what makes me whole
and makes me living.

00:26:39.160 --> 00:26:42.460 align:middle line:84%
>> Would you say that
on a regular basis,

00:26:42.460 --> 00:26:48.360 align:middle line:84%
you consciously connect to
the Akashic field every day?

00:26:48.360 --> 00:26:52.690 align:middle line:84%
>> Not consciously,
subconsciously, deeply,

00:26:52.690 --> 00:26:55.130 align:middle line:90%
spiritually, yes.

00:26:55.130 --> 00:26:57.920 align:middle line:84%
I have a little place
here in my house,

00:26:57.920 --> 00:27:00.560 align:middle line:84%
but it could have been
anywhere else, which

00:27:00.560 --> 00:27:05.120 align:middle line:84%
is a little shrine or a
little place of meditation,

00:27:05.120 --> 00:27:09.530 align:middle line:84%
has a Buddha in it for a
feeling of timelessness

00:27:09.530 --> 00:27:14.450 align:middle line:84%
and which is a beautiful
view opening to a valley that

00:27:14.450 --> 00:27:19.890 align:middle line:84%
has been not only permanently
inhabited but also permanently

00:27:19.890 --> 00:27:20.690 align:middle line:90%
worked.

00:27:20.690 --> 00:27:23.810 align:middle line:84%
The land has been permanently
worked for 5,000 years

00:27:23.810 --> 00:27:27.650 align:middle line:84%
from the Etruscan times,
which was before the Romans.

00:27:27.650 --> 00:27:33.170 align:middle line:84%
And this valley has something
very human about it.

00:27:33.170 --> 00:27:38.550 align:middle line:84%
It shows the interaction of
people, of humanity with nature,

00:27:38.550 --> 00:27:41.840 align:middle line:84%
not as something that
we impose on nature.

00:27:41.840 --> 00:27:46.010 align:middle line:84%
And new settlements very often
are industrial settlements

00:27:46.010 --> 00:27:49.700 align:middle line:84%
or just massive
living settlements,

00:27:49.700 --> 00:27:53.150 align:middle line:84%
which are something that you
put over, place on nature,

00:27:53.150 --> 00:27:54.810 align:middle line:90%
doesn't really belong to it.

00:27:54.810 --> 00:27:58.290 align:middle line:84%
Here I have a sense that
we belong to nature,

00:27:58.290 --> 00:28:00.630 align:middle line:84%
that this valley
has been existing.

00:28:00.630 --> 00:28:06.310 align:middle line:84%
And it is part of humanity
to be part of this valley.

00:28:06.310 --> 00:28:12.370 align:middle line:84%
So I feel that my experience is
one which gives me the strength

00:28:12.370 --> 00:28:16.600 align:middle line:84%
to move forward, gives me the
strength also to have whatever

00:28:16.600 --> 00:28:18.370 align:middle line:90%
insight I possess.

00:28:18.370 --> 00:28:21.340 align:middle line:84%
And people claim
that I could show

00:28:21.340 --> 00:28:23.620 align:middle line:90%
them the way to some insights.

00:28:23.620 --> 00:28:28.000 align:middle line:84%
And that is something not that I
manufacture, not that I create,

00:28:28.000 --> 00:28:30.490 align:middle line:90%
not that I do consciously.

00:28:30.490 --> 00:28:36.280 align:middle line:84%
This connection that I have to
the field is a subconscious,

00:28:36.280 --> 00:28:39.140 align:middle line:90%
is a spontaneous connection.

00:28:39.140 --> 00:28:41.530 align:middle line:84%
I don't think we can
have it any other way.

00:28:41.530 --> 00:28:44.620 align:middle line:84%
I think we must be in a
different altered state

00:28:44.620 --> 00:28:47.560 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness in
order to really connect

00:28:47.560 --> 00:28:50.110 align:middle line:84%
to the field, the
ordinary state--

00:28:50.110 --> 00:28:52.720 align:middle line:84%
And we can measure this
by the EEG patterns,

00:28:52.720 --> 00:28:54.550 align:middle line:84%
the electroencephalographic
patterns,

00:28:54.550 --> 00:28:57.740 align:middle line:84%
in ordinary states of
delta, for example.

00:28:57.740 --> 00:28:59.560 align:middle line:90%
We see the world around us.

00:28:59.560 --> 00:29:04.240 align:middle line:84%
And we go down deeper down
to alpha and beta and theta.

00:29:04.240 --> 00:29:06.310 align:middle line:84%
And then I think
we can also have

00:29:06.310 --> 00:29:10.930 align:middle line:84%
experiences that go beyond
the everyday sites around us.

00:29:10.930 --> 00:29:13.700 align:middle line:90%
We are in a deeper dimension.

00:29:13.700 --> 00:29:15.160 align:middle line:90%
I connect through music.

00:29:15.160 --> 00:29:18.790 align:middle line:84%
I connect through ideas,
through great literature,

00:29:18.790 --> 00:29:22.380 align:middle line:84%
through enjoying
nature, and also

00:29:22.380 --> 00:29:27.090 align:middle line:84%
through enjoying creating
theories that makes sense to me.

00:29:27.090 --> 00:29:28.530 align:middle line:90%
And I try to communicate.

00:29:28.530 --> 00:29:30.850 align:middle line:84%
And I hope it makes
sense to others.

00:29:30.850 --> 00:29:33.160 align:middle line:84%
That is the experience
that I have.

00:29:33.160 --> 00:29:34.800 align:middle line:84%
And that is the
experience that I

00:29:34.800 --> 00:29:37.860 align:middle line:84%
pursue with all
the time and energy

00:29:37.860 --> 00:29:40.190 align:middle line:90%
to have at my disposition.

00:29:40.190 --> 00:29:44.790 align:middle line:84%
>> So when you connect, if
I'm following you correctly,

00:29:44.790 --> 00:29:48.885 align:middle line:84%
it feels like this
tremendous sense of oneness?

00:29:48.885 --> 00:29:52.770 align:middle line:84%
>> There are many
ways to it, many ways.

00:29:52.770 --> 00:29:55.500 align:middle line:84%
Carl Jung already
has pointed out

00:29:55.500 --> 00:29:57.630 align:middle line:84%
that our everyday
consciousness is just

00:29:57.630 --> 00:30:01.050 align:middle line:84%
a thin layer over a
deeper consciousness,

00:30:01.050 --> 00:30:05.010 align:middle line:84%
our psyche is much more than
the surface consciousness

00:30:05.010 --> 00:30:10.930 align:middle line:84%
of looking at things and events
and interacting with them.

00:30:10.930 --> 00:30:12.430 align:middle line:90%
We have a deeper sense.

00:30:12.430 --> 00:30:18.180 align:middle line:84%
So we are actually connected
by nature, by the universe.

00:30:18.180 --> 00:30:20.520 align:middle line:90%
We are connected being.

00:30:20.520 --> 00:30:23.290 align:middle line:90%
But we eliminate it.

00:30:23.290 --> 00:30:26.050 align:middle line:84%
Consciousness is
not only an avenue

00:30:26.050 --> 00:30:29.960 align:middle line:84%
to a deeper connection, a
deeper dimension of the world.

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:31.900 align:middle line:90%
It's also a filter.

00:30:31.900 --> 00:30:34.480 align:middle line:84%
Everyday consciousness
is a filter.

00:30:34.480 --> 00:30:40.240 align:middle line:84%
It filters out what we could be
feeling, what we could perceive

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:44.530 align:middle line:84%
by reducing it only to
the everyday happenings

00:30:44.530 --> 00:30:48.040 align:middle line:84%
to the items that are
immediately close to us.

00:30:48.040 --> 00:30:52.360 align:middle line:84%
Einstein, Schrödinger, Jung,
all the great scientists

00:30:52.360 --> 00:30:55.000 align:middle line:90%
have come across this notion.

00:30:55.000 --> 00:31:00.100 align:middle line:84%
Consciousness is not only
a new avenue, an opening,

00:31:00.100 --> 00:31:03.430 align:middle line:90%
it's also a restriction.

00:31:03.430 --> 00:31:07.040 align:middle line:84%
But it's up to us
whether we stay

00:31:07.040 --> 00:31:11.800 align:middle line:84%
within that kind of restricted
everyday consciousness

00:31:11.800 --> 00:31:13.060 align:middle line:90%
or whether we go deeper.

00:31:13.060 --> 00:31:14.890 align:middle line:90%
We can all go deeper.

00:31:14.890 --> 00:31:19.120 align:middle line:84%
We can all enter
into altered states.

00:31:19.120 --> 00:31:21.130 align:middle line:90%
Prayer does that.

00:31:21.130 --> 00:31:23.260 align:middle line:90%
Meditation does that.

00:31:23.260 --> 00:31:24.820 align:middle line:90%
Art does that.

00:31:24.820 --> 00:31:27.550 align:middle line:90%
Nature does that.

00:31:27.550 --> 00:31:29.880 align:middle line:84%
And so our culture
and the highest levels

00:31:29.880 --> 00:31:34.560 align:middle line:84%
of cultural expression are
these expressions of oneness,

00:31:34.560 --> 00:31:36.030 align:middle line:90%
of belonging.

00:31:36.030 --> 00:31:40.930 align:middle line:84%
And when young people today they
talk about unconditional love,

00:31:40.930 --> 00:31:43.060 align:middle line:90%
they talk about this experience.

00:31:43.060 --> 00:31:45.340 align:middle line:84%
You can't just talk
about unconditional love.

00:31:45.340 --> 00:31:46.840 align:middle line:90%
You don't know what it means.

00:31:46.840 --> 00:31:48.040 align:middle line:90%
You must feel it.

00:31:48.040 --> 00:31:49.810 align:middle line:90%
You must experience it.

00:31:49.810 --> 00:31:54.570 align:middle line:84%
And people who do that, who
really talk about it, who really

00:31:54.570 --> 00:32:00.800 align:middle line:84%
are a sense of this
love, projected,

00:32:00.800 --> 00:32:05.390 align:middle line:84%
created toward
receiving this love also

00:32:05.390 --> 00:32:09.710 align:middle line:84%
from everything, that is then
they are in another dimension.

00:32:09.710 --> 00:32:13.110 align:middle line:84%
They're entering into the true
dimension, which you and I,

00:32:13.110 --> 00:32:14.990 align:middle line:84%
we can talk about the
Akashic dimension.

00:32:14.990 --> 00:32:17.240 align:middle line:90%
It's also the quantum dimension.

00:32:17.240 --> 00:32:20.180 align:middle line:84%
It's the new science,
new spirituality.

00:32:20.180 --> 00:32:22.820 align:middle line:84%
The two things are
no longer separate.

00:32:22.820 --> 00:32:26.690 align:middle line:84%
The new science bears
out many of the insights

00:32:26.690 --> 00:32:29.660 align:middle line:84%
of great spirituality of
the thousands of years.

00:32:29.660 --> 00:32:30.770 align:middle line:90%
I'm exploring this.

00:32:30.770 --> 00:32:33.690 align:middle line:84%
This is one of my tasks,
one of my mission,

00:32:33.690 --> 00:32:39.830 align:middle line:84%
a sense of exploring the great
truths that have been expressed

00:32:39.830 --> 00:32:42.170 align:middle line:84%
coming to the fore
thousands of years

00:32:42.170 --> 00:32:46.670 align:middle line:84%
ago, how they are transmitted
today in science because they

00:32:46.670 --> 00:32:48.980 align:middle line:84%
are there in science,
whether it comes

00:32:48.980 --> 00:32:53.660 align:middle line:84%
to healthy living, good eating,
good rapport with each other,

00:32:53.660 --> 00:32:54.740 align:middle line:90%
with nature.

00:32:54.740 --> 00:32:56.360 align:middle line:90%
It has all been known.

00:32:56.360 --> 00:33:00.000 align:middle line:84%
And now the new biology, the
quantum biology, the quantum

00:33:00.000 --> 00:33:03.990 align:middle line:84%
psychology, the consciousness
research, the new physics

00:33:03.990 --> 00:33:08.070 align:middle line:84%
telling us that this indeed is
not just imagination, that's

00:33:08.070 --> 00:33:09.966 align:middle line:90%
the way things are.

00:33:09.966 --> 00:33:15.100 align:middle line:84%
>> Many people assume that they
