00:33:28.195 --> 00:33:30.970 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, that is a mistake.

00:33:30.970 --> 00:33:36.870 align:middle line:84%
That is a dangerous fallacy
of the modern mindset.

00:33:36.870 --> 00:33:39.690 align:middle line:84%
These people consciously
or subconsciously

00:33:39.690 --> 00:33:43.500 align:middle line:84%
operate on the Newtonian
paradigm, which says,

00:33:43.500 --> 00:33:48.030 align:middle line:84%
