it is just imagination.

00:33:57.630 --> 00:33:59.780 align:middle line:84%
So this is the normal
paradigm, which

00:33:59.780 --> 00:34:02.550 align:middle line:90%
is no longer valid in science.

00:34:02.550 --> 00:34:06.460 align:middle line:84%
But it's still
powerful in society.

00:34:06.460 --> 00:34:09.070 align:middle line:84%
People who feel
like you are saying,

00:34:09.070 --> 00:34:11.739 align:middle line:84%
they can't go
beyond the surface,

00:34:11.739 --> 00:34:14.500 align:middle line:84%
they operate on the
basis of this paradigm.

00:34:14.500 --> 00:34:20.679 align:middle line:84%
Very often what we believe
influences what we actually see.

00:34:20.679 --> 00:34:25.540 align:middle line:84%
Very often we don't even see or
perceive what we don't believe.

00:34:25.540 --> 00:34:27.310 align:middle line:84%
And when these
people don't believe

00:34:27.310 --> 00:34:31.690 align:middle line:84%
that they can go beyond it,
they don't go beyond it.

00:34:31.690 --> 00:34:32.840 align:middle line:90%
They can't.

00:34:32.840 --> 00:34:34.300 align:middle line:90%
We have to open up.

