00:34:42.429 --> 00:34:45.650 align:middle line:84%
It's more than the
world as usual.

00:34:45.650 --> 00:34:47.199 align:middle line:90%
There is more to this world.

00:34:47.199 --> 00:34:48.909 align:middle line:84%
There are more
possibilities also,

00:34:48.909 --> 00:34:52.550 align:middle line:84%
more dangers but
more opportunities.

