what we thought it was.

00:41:42.560 --> 00:41:46.920 align:middle line:84%
One of the greatest
contemporary scientists,

00:41:46.920 --> 00:41:50.220 align:middle line:84%
he died a few decades
ago, Max Planck.

00:41:50.220 --> 00:41:53.290 align:middle line:84%
He was the father of
the atomic theory.

00:41:53.290 --> 00:41:56.720 align:middle line:84%
He said in one of
his last talks--

00:41:56.720 --> 00:41:59.390 align:middle line:84%
