00:42:20.180 --> 00:42:23.260 align:middle line:84%
I think the other great
physicists today would certainly

00:42:23.260 --> 00:42:24.500 align:middle line:90%
agree with that.

00:42:24.500 --> 00:42:26.510 align:middle line:84%
But that's a shock
for other people.

00:42:26.510 --> 00:42:28.210 align:middle line:84%
What do you mean
there's no matter?

00:42:28.210 --> 00:42:31.684 align:middle line:90%
What is there then?

00:42:31.684 --> 00:42:34.570 align:middle line:84%
What we find and Max
Planck said and I

00:42:34.570 --> 00:42:38.830 align:middle line:84%
agree with that, what we
