with each other,

00:42:42.680 --> 00:42:46.690 align:middle line:84%
interacting, building
higher levels of vibration.

00:42:46.690 --> 00:42:50.030 align:middle line:90%
Our body is a vibrating system.

00:42:50.030 --> 00:42:54.110 align:middle line:84%
And the proton and the neutron
in the nucleus of the electron

00:42:54.110 --> 00:42:55.850 align:middle line:90%
