00:42:55.850 --> 00:42:59.450 align:middle line:84%
And they build higher
and higher level systems.

00:42:59.450 --> 00:43:05.050 align:middle line:84%
The whole universe is a
vibrating whole system.

00:43:05.050 --> 00:43:08.380 align:middle line:84%
Very, very different idea
from little hard pieces

00:43:08.380 --> 00:43:13.570 align:middle line:84%
of matter that Democritus,
