00:43:23.590 --> 00:43:25.720 align:middle line:90%
It's all vibration.

00:43:25.720 --> 00:43:31.630 align:middle line:84%
It's all coincided,
coherent waves building

00:43:31.630 --> 00:43:34.130 align:middle line:90%
higher and higher-level waves.

00:43:34.130 --> 00:43:38.944 align:middle line:84%
It's a C. It's a quantum
C, information C,

00:43:38.944 --> 00:43:45.050 align:middle line:84%
not a bit of space and time
in which matter moves around.

00:43:45.050 --> 00:43:49.330 align:middle line:10%
>> Ervin, if we could talk
a little bit more about what

00:43:49.330 --> 00:43:54.790 align:middle line:10%
critical point you believe
