So that's a technical term.

00:43:59.720 --> 00:44:01.660 align:middle line:10%
It comes from the
physical sciences,

00:44:01.660 --> 00:44:08.880 align:middle line:10%
from cybernetics, also
from physical chemistry.

00:44:08.880 --> 00:44:14.720 align:middle line:10%
But it just means that there
is a sudden change, a forking

00:44:14.720 --> 00:44:17.660 align:middle line:10%
in the past of our development.

00:44:17.660 --> 00:44:19.370 align:middle line:10%
We all evolve.

00:44:19.370 --> 00:44:21.770 align:middle line:10%
