00:44:39.110 --> 00:44:40.160 align:middle line:90%
Why not humanity?

00:44:40.160 --> 00:44:41.750 align:middle line:90%
But we have consciousness.

00:44:41.750 --> 00:44:45.200 align:middle line:84%
We can recognize who we
are and what we are doing.

00:44:45.200 --> 00:44:48.710 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, we can
consciously change our ways.

00:44:48.710 --> 00:44:53.570 align:middle line:10%
But we are at a point
where our evolution needs

00:44:53.570 --> 00:44:57.910 align:middle line:10%
to be taken into our hand
because we have gone off

00:44:57.910 --> 00:45:01.520 align:middle line:10%
in a wrong way, not just
in the past few years

00:45:01.520 --> 00:45:05.080 align:middle line:10%
but in the past 150,
200 years perhaps.

00:45:05.080 --> 00:45:12.010 align:middle line:84%
We have put our trust into
a material-based technology.

00:45:12.010 --> 00:45:14.510 align:middle line:84%
We can create the
world around us.

00:45:14.510 --> 00:45:17.840 align:middle line:84%
We can make what we
want, what we need.

00:45:17.840 --> 00:45:19.870 align:middle line:84%
And never mind the
world, never mind

00:45:19.870 --> 00:45:22.540 align:middle line:90%
the effect, the consequences.

00:45:22.540 --> 00:45:24.850 align:middle line:84%
Don't think of yourself
as being in the world.

00:45:24.850 --> 00:45:29.650 align:middle line:84%
Think of yourself as being
above the world, master world.

00:45:29.650 --> 00:45:33.950 align:middle line:84%
That has been the ruling
principle in the modern world,

00:45:33.950 --> 00:45:36.160 align:middle line:84%
especially, first of all,
in the Western world.

00:45:36.160 --> 00:45:39.580 align:middle line:84%
But then in the 20th century,
through the two world wars,

00:45:39.580 --> 00:45:44.350 align:middle line:84%
this kind of thinking spread
also to the East and as much

00:45:44.350 --> 00:45:47.590 align:middle line:84%
as it could spread also to
the less developed countries

00:45:47.590 --> 00:45:49.640 align:middle line:90%
in the south.

