of that system and not

00:46:08.480 --> 00:46:09.560 align:middle line:90%
the other parts.

00:46:09.560 --> 00:46:12.560 align:middle line:84%
The part is what
our interests are.

00:46:12.560 --> 00:46:17.510 align:middle line:84%
Our power, our wealth is
what we want to promote.

00:46:17.510 --> 00:46:19.640 align:middle line:90%
Never mind the rest.

00:46:19.640 --> 00:46:23.420 align:middle line:84%
And by doing this, there's
a technical term as well

00:46:23.420 --> 00:46:24.530 align:middle line:90%
like bifurcation.

00:46:24.530 --> 00:46:26.480 align:middle line:90%
It's being suboptimizing.

00:46:26.480 --> 00:46:29.450 align:middle line:84%
When you optimize
a system, you make

00:46:29.450 --> 00:46:33.240 align:middle line:84%
it work as well as possible,
the best possible way.

00:46:33.240 --> 00:46:36.920 align:middle line:84%
When you suboptimize, it means
that you are only optimizing

00:46:36.920 --> 00:46:39.920 align:middle line:90%
a part of the system.

00:46:39.920 --> 00:46:47.110 align:middle line:10%
And that part can flourish
but for a time only.

00:46:47.110 --> 00:46:50.020 align:middle line:10%
Sooner or later, it
becomes kind of a cancer

00:46:50.020 --> 00:46:53.320 align:middle line:10%
because that system
begins to take

00:46:53.320 --> 00:46:56.860 align:middle line:10%
the resources to use the
energy that would also

00:46:56.860 --> 00:46:59.220 align:middle line:10%
be needed for others.

00:46:59.220 --> 00:47:03.030 align:middle line:10%
It becomes kind of a
blister, and then later

00:47:03.030 --> 00:47:05.880 align:middle line:10%
on a dangerous cancer.

00:47:05.880 --> 00:47:10.770 align:middle line:10%
We have to return to the view
that this system in which we

00:47:10.770 --> 00:47:16.230 align:middle line:10%
