00:47:37.230 --> 00:47:39.840 align:middle line:84%
gains with the
material instruments

00:47:39.840 --> 00:47:43.680 align:middle line:84%
that we had can
provide well-being

00:47:43.680 --> 00:47:47.130 align:middle line:84%
for a short period
