00:47:47.130 --> 00:47:51.360 align:middle line:84%
But it's dangerous in the longer
term for the great majority.

00:47:51.360 --> 00:47:53.310 align:middle line:90%
That's the point we are at.

00:47:53.310 --> 00:47:56.760 align:middle line:84%
The sooner we realize
this, the sooner

00:47:56.760 --> 00:47:59.700 align:middle line:84%
