That would be very tragic.

00:48:17.910 --> 00:48:18.910 align:middle line:90%
That would be dangerous.

00:48:18.910 --> 00:48:21.054 align:middle line:90%
Let's use it to learn.

00:48:21.054 --> 00:48:23.710 align:middle line:90%
Learn from what is happening.

00:48:23.710 --> 00:48:28.690 align:middle line:84%
Learn that we can be a
highly fragile system that

00:48:28.690 --> 00:48:30.940 align:middle line:90%
can easily go extinct even.

00:48:30.940 --> 00:48:34.760 align:middle line:84%
Let's learn and do
something better.

00:48:34.760 --> 00:48:37.990 align:middle line:84%
Something better is something
what everything in the universe

00:48:37.990 --> 00:48:43.030 align:middle line:84%
is doing around us,
building coherent systems.

00:48:43.030 --> 00:48:46.420 align:middle line:10%
That's a very, very
important term, "coherence."

00:48:46.420 --> 00:48:49.180 align:middle line:10%
It means that all
parts of a system

00:48:49.180 --> 00:48:51.640 align:middle line:10%
are interacting with
all other parts.

00:48:51.640 --> 00:48:54.590 align:middle line:10%
And together, they
maintain the system.

00:48:54.590 --> 00:48:56.380 align:middle line:10%
Let's look at the whole system.

00:48:56.380 --> 00:48:59.590 align:middle line:10%
What is the whole system for us?

00:48:59.590 --> 00:49:01.660 align:middle line:10%
Obviously, the whole
system is a universe.

00:49:01.660 --> 00:49:06.100 align:middle line:10%
But what really concerns us
is what we call the biosphere.

00:49:06.100 --> 00:49:08.710 align:middle line:10%
The sphere of life on Earth.

00:49:08.710 --> 00:49:10.660 align:middle line:10%
That's the system.

00:49:10.660 --> 00:49:15.340 align:middle line:10%
If we can make that flourish,
if we can make it sustainable,

00:49:15.340 --> 00:49:17.020 align:middle line:10%
then we can live in it.

00:49:17.020 --> 00:49:19.750 align:middle line:10%
And we can flourish ourselves.

00:49:19.750 --> 00:49:23.620 align:middle line:10%
If we try to flourish at
the expense of that system,

00:49:23.620 --> 00:49:25.690 align:middle line:10%
then sooner or later,
it will break down.

00:49:25.690 --> 00:49:28.040 align:middle line:10%
And it makes us break down.

00:49:28.040 --> 00:49:31.000 align:middle line:10%
So here we are at a
historic turning point,

00:49:31.000 --> 00:49:33.190 align:middle line:10%
a historic turning
point where we recognize

00:49:33.190 --> 00:49:35.860 align:middle line:10%
some age-old insights.

00:49:35.860 --> 00:49:39.610 align:middle line:10%
But we recognize that this is a
precondition of our existence.

